Available Tools: set_temperature | get_temperature | set_mode | get_schedule
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "device_id": "string", "temperature": "number|null", "mode": "string|null" }
Response Schema: { "device_id": "string", "current_temp": "number", "target_temp": "number", "mode": "string" }
---
Question: Adjust the kitchen thermostat to 23 degrees for cooking dinner.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "therm_kit_09", "temperature": 23.0, "mode": null }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_kit_09", "current_temp": 20.1, "target_temp": 23.0, "mode": "heat" }

Question: Lower the attic temperature setting to 18 degrees before bed.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "therm_att_10", "temperature": 18.0, "mode": null }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_att_10", "current_temp": 22.4, "target_temp": 18.0, "mode": "cool" }

Question: Raise the sunroom heater target to 25 degrees for the morning sun.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "therm_sun_11", "temperature": 25.0, "mode": null }
Response: { "device_id": "therm_sun_11", "current_temp": 19.5, "target_temp": 25.0, "mode": "heat" }

Question: Decrease the library cooling setpoint to 20 degrees during study time.
